      "matters": "ACCOUNTING PETITION RE: FEES, FINAL DISTRIBUTION<br>Off Calendar Apr-23-2009 Granted Per Written Order<br>MINI MINUTES: Appearances: Richard Wall for Angela Oliva (Petitioner).<br><br>The Court stated that it reviewed the petition, that there was a concern with the distribution going directly to the Beneficiaries and that the proper manner was to have the assets be distributed to the Trust. The Court directed Mr. Wall to submit an amended order reflecting that the assets are being distributed to him as the Trustee. The Court granted the petition, (subject to receipt and review of the amended order).  <br><br>Judge: David L. Ballati. Reporter: Susan Lee, CSR#4280. Clerk: Rosie Noguera. Bailiff: Deputy R. Harris.<br>",
